Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.27,0:00:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.18,0:00:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.52,0:00:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.63,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.94,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.18,0:00:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.32,0:01:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這邊,快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.45,0:02:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是稀奇了,一個人來看電影?\N這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?瞧你臉色蒼白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要喝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這條大壞狗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳,我已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-那我走了\N-等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.32,0:03:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,難道你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.79,0:03:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#49 三鷹拼死特訓!\N怕狗還能談戀愛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心,我抓得很緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.31,0:03:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎也真是的\N居然藏了那麼多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?定期車票?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西是從哪裡撿回來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裡面有沒有啤酒券?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,都是一些無聊的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你怎麼把它放進口袋了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把它還給失主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是這樣,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉谷站,涉谷站到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-讓你久等了\N-不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下\N妳真的願意幫我的忙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於我怕狗的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要給你來個特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特…特訓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,不論多麼嚴格的特訓\N我都會撐過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,在那之前\N我們先去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對,我希望找個能喝酒的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先從這個開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忠犬八公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去摸摸它的頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去摸它的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是附近有這麼多人在看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說什麼都肯做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-那傢伙在幹嘛?\N-像個白痴似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-真是夠了\N-春天也快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.41,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-不會吧\N-真是難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來光靠我一個人是解決不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要告訴音無小姐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然?你知道什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有稍微察覺到\N五代好像以前就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.04,0:06:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到三鷹教練會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家有沒有什麼好辦法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不治好他怕狗的毛病\N連惣一郎都無法接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹真的很拼命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我也來助他一臂之力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然我也願意幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然決定了,那就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的體驗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你會那麼怕狗\N若無法把原因找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒辦法擬定對策的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你回想往事或許很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,如果你繼續逃避的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧,我跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時我還是個小學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,又打出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,又是那隻狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.63,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用問嗎?\N當然要去把球拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,小狗,小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡,這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊,這裡這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,這裡這裡,好聰明喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,快回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.34,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直被困在狗屋裡\N直到主人來餵牠晚餐時才得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可以給我當禮物帶回去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心,請包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個禮拜後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來重現一次\N你小時候的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.07,0:09:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗叫聲,國王的耳朵\N是老太婆的麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(時鐘坡網球俱樂部)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的重要的事是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好照顧這些狗狗唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你得稍微習慣跟它們相處才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會認輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,教練,你在看哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.51,0:11:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹他怎麼了?\N看起來好憔悴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四題,抬頭狂吠的小狗\N和低頭躲在門後低吟的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一隻比較危險?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩隻都很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是低吟的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一隻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,低吟的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-接下來第五題\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,65分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也蠻拼的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已經敢摸狗布偶娃娃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.99,0:12:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊\N那接下來差不多要用真狗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,你要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.95,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,我想去一下書店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好安靜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.43,0:13:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,今天朱美他們都不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!那麼說果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.95,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,無論如何我都要渡過這關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這塊肉好硬哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,這麼一來音無小姐也會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教練,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊什麼啊\N你怎麼連一口都沒吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天取消吧,再找別的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我要練,而且非練不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間也差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,那麼走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間到了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來三瓶啤酒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們不陪我一起去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.14,0:15:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是任何難關都能渡過的人\N自己一個人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.21,0:15:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會在這裡等你回來\N你不可以作弊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,這是為了你自己好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,不可以依賴別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-加油喔\N-好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.54,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,16號,博美犬博克\N一歲三個月大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是17號…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.56,0:16:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,該怎麼說呢\N他真的很拼命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,怎麼到現在還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶,已經超過一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會不會是溜掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿他沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有好一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我現在看到狗\N已經不會怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是再休息一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒面子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的膝蓋給你當枕頭吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就別跟我客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,在這裡不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就乖乖躺下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員真是個幸福的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.19,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳,我已經好很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開車送妳回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了,我要直接去上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是蹺班會被炒魷魚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員他們等一下也會來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢喔,他們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去叫他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼,快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?惣一郎呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡,我把牠交給了三鷹教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.86,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個妳拿一下,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-怎麼回事?\N-不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,冷靜一點\N三鷹,你要冷靜下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想一下之前做的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.75,0:19:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七題,小狗一直靠過來\N要怎麼逃脫呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一,拼命的跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.49,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二,拿棒子打小狗的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三,裝作沒事似的走過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確答案是三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝作沒事似的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.52,0:19:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不可以這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,繩子給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-走…走了嗎?\N-走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,抱歉\N接下來交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他臨時有事走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得心頭悶悶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.09,0:21:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在三鷹的心裡依然殘留著\N小時候可怕的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把這個傷口治癒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能消除他對狗的恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.60,0:21:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此,要再度重現那種體驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後去克服它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.18,0:22:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,找到球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼,只是一隻小狗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這樣我應該有辦法應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.78,0:22:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下應該能讓三鷹\N對自己很有信心才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.52,0:22:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成功了,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,真的好可怕哦\N居然發生了車禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.51,0:23:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,真的很可怕\N都怪我恍恍惚惚的才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.15,0:23:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近你的身體好像不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.89,0:23:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,現在又滿身大汗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.29,0:23:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是乾淨的,請拿去擦擦汗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.63,0:23:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好意思,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.06,0:23:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,有啊,還有空房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.17,0:23:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你這樣說太突然了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.20,0:23:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.94,0:24:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「響子一見鍾情!?\N一刻館出現奇怪的傢伙」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.71,0:24:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你怎麼還能這麼冷靜的\N唸著下一回的標題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.39,0:24:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.30,0:24:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.08,0:24:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.62,0:24:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.99,0:24:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.72,0:24:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.53,0:25:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.74,0:25:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.88,0:25:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.92,0:25:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy

